2. cs.GR (Graphics) - The paper proposes a novel alpha-matte boundary defocus model to generate training data, which involves modeling the defocus spread effect. This is related to graphics and image processing. 
3. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with the problem of multi-focus image fusion, which is a common problem in multimedia applications. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The proposed MMF-Net is a cascaded boundary aware convolutional network, which involves deep learning techniques and is related to artificial intelligence. 
5. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The proposed MMF-Net is a deep learning-based method, which involves machine learning techniques.
